{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/no-invalid-double-slash-comments/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/no-empty-source/","description":"no-extra-semicolons 禁止额外的分号。 此规则忽略在 Less mixins 之后的分号。 命令行中的 --fix 选项可以自动修复此规则报告的所有问题。 选项 true 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规：","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"no-extra-semicolons\"><a href=\"#no-extra-semicolons\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>no-extra-semicolons</h1>\n<p>禁止额外的分号。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**             ↑\n *          这个分号 */</span></code></pre>\n<p>此规则忽略在 Less mixins 之后的分号。</p>\n<p><a href=\"../../../../user-guide/cli/#%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF\">命令行</a>中的 <code>--fix</code> 选项可以自动修复此规则报告的所有问题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<h3 id=\"true\"><a href=\"#true\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>true</code></h3>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"x.css\"</span>;;</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"x.css\"</span>;\n;</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  ;<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n  ;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: red;\n}\n;\n<span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">b</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: white;\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"x.css\"</span>;</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/no-extra-semicolons.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/no-extra-semicolons/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/no-extra-semicolons/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/no-extra-semicolons/index.html.f6d3567688e5d45d79929ece0930eed7.json"}